    <section name="Getting Started with Jadabs-CLDC">
      <p>In order to get started with the Jadabs-CLDC bundles developed during
         the semester work is suggested that the final MIDlet application 
         <a href="multiproject/smartmessenger/index.html">SmartMessenger</a>
         application is started first. The application can be used 
         to verify that the bundles have been correctly built and the 
         Maven repository is in a consistent state. Following steps must
         be executed:</p>
         
