         <li><a href="bootstrap.html#buildjadabs">Build Jadabs Bundles</a></li>
         <li><a href="bootstrap.html#jadabscldc">Check-out Jadabs-CLDC from CVS</a></li>
         <li><a href="bootstrap.html#antenna">Installing Maven-Antenna-Plugin</a></li>
         <li><a href="bootstrap.html#wtk">Install Java Wireless Toolkit</a></li>
         <li><a href="bootstrap.html#buildjadabscldc">Build all Jadabs-CLDC</a></li>
         <li><a href="smartmessenger.html">Install SmartMessenger on mobile phone</a></li>         
      </ol>
